reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Get your money's worth
reviews.reviewText: A really nice budget smart watch that has so many functions. Wear for several days, works well and battery holds pretty good. Big and clear screen, easy to see and use. Love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great watch. Great price.
reviews.reviewText: I really like this watch. It was an expensive, Call quality is super clear, And it was very easy to hook up. The band is very comfortable.And the signs of the screen is excellent. I'm a guy with very big hands and fingers. And it's easy for me to navigate on this large size watch face.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Watch came with 50% battery charge. Opened up immediately and charged with no problems. Super easy set up. Seems to be working perfectly and is light weight making it a comfortable wear. Comes with 1 year manufacturer warranty which was a pleasant surprise as it was quite inexpensive.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: First, this is a big watch but who cares! Large, responsive, easy to read screen with a bigger battery and heavy duty strap. The Hanfit app is easy to setup and pair with the watch. I used my spare phone hooked up to home internet to save data on my pay as you go fone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So versatile and lightweight
reviews.reviewText: This watch looks pretty awesome. I was surprised by how lightweight it is but so functional. The screen is very bright. It is easy to use. I don’t know how it holds up long term, but so far, it works well for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good features for the price
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to get a watch for my dad and ended up selecting this watch. Upon receiving it, the first reaction I got was this felt worth more than the price I paid. The watch face was bright, and the heft was nice on the arm.The watch did not feel too plasticky. We tested out the water resistance on the watch, and it survived the test without any issues.The screen is nice and bright and can be used outdoors. The watch is responsive enough to use day to day. The watch comes with some apps preinstalled that can be fairly useful like sleep tracking and even a remote control for your cell phone's camera.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great smart watch!
reviews.reviewText: The watch display is really nice. The apps and notifications work great. Comfortable band but it is bit bulky for my 17 yr old son's wrist. Overall, highly recommend as it is great for the price point.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing customer support
reviews.reviewText: My son dropped it and it fell apart. Not really fall resistant. Received on the 29th of December so not even a month in. Reached out to the company and still haven’t received a response. 2 stars because it was a nice watch and had nice features when it wasn’t broken.*update. The company replied to my email and will send a replacement. Will update pictures with new watch when received. Received replacement. Satisfied with how easy and fast everything was.
